description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salisbury Maternity service is looking for a resourceful and motivated senior midwife to join the leadership team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Within the service we put mothers and families, and their safety, at the centre of our thinking and work as partners in their care.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The successful applicant will have an important place in the midwifery management team. You will have a role supporting the labour ward area, managing safe care and supporting the midwifery team to develop and learn and to do their best as autonomous professionals at all times. You will also be required to have excellent computer skills to be able to continue to drive the maternity digital agenda forward.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Within the role you will be expected to have a management role and will be supported by the Head of Maternity and Neonatal Services to develop and progress in your career. The post holder will be expected to influence in a positive way and role model the Trust values and behaviours.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It is essential that the post holder remains a visible, clinical leader and contributes to the duty manager role and rota. Clinical competence in a lead role is essential&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will enjoy a high level of autonomy in this role and report directly to the Head of Maternity service.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Vicki Marston&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Deputy Head of Maternity and Maternity Services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address vicki.marston1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 01722 425183&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An informal discussion with the deputy HOM is welcomed and is strongly recommended..&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please contact Vicki Marston Deputy Head of Midwifery and Neonatal Services&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;email: vicki.marston1@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Phone: 01722 427171&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
